## 3. Database functions (Postgres)

| Function | Role |
|----------|------|
| `get_latest_decision_run(p_case_id uuid)` | Returns latest `case_decision_runs` row for UI / orchestration. |
| `get_effective_entitlement(p_case_id uuid)` | JSON effective plan/features for a case. |
| `get_case_eligibility(p_case_id uuid)` | **SECURITY DEFINER** eligibility JSON for gating (self-serve vs decision vs escalation); aligns resolved ids with report flow. |
| `match_public_decisions` / `match_public_decisions_threshold` | pgvector precedent retrieval over `public_decisions.embedding`. |
| `match_regulatory_clauses` | **Overloaded:** (embedding, match_count) uses `<->` ranking; (embedding, match_count, threshold) and `match_regulatory_clauses_threshold` add threshold filtering — confirm which signature edge functions call. |
| `run_validation_v1(p_extract_run_id uuid)` | Rule-based validation insert; returns new validation id. |
| `set_case_intake_version` | BEFORE INSERT trigger helper for monotonic `version`. |
| `set_updated_at` | Generic `updated_at` touch trigger. |

